stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Anonymous

    Anonymous --> Authenticating: login submitted
    Authenticating --> Authenticated: token valid
    Authenticating --> Anonymous: token invalid

    Authenticated --> Refreshing: token nearing expiry
    Refreshing --> Authenticated: refresh success
    Refreshing --> Expired: refresh failed

    Authenticated --> Expired: idle timeout
    Expired --> Anonymous: logout complete
    Expired --> Authenticating: re-login
